description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity for a Specialist Doctor in Old Age Psychiatry will become available. The post holder will become an integral member of the Old Age Psychiatry team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post holder will join the existing Old Age Psychiatry team in an innovative, well established, well organised and comprehensive mental health service for older adults covering Bridgend County Borough.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The total catchment population of the Bridgend County Borough area is 30,000 adults over the age of 65 years. This specialty doctor post is part of the established Old Age Psychiatry team providing psychiatric care to community and hospital inpatients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder responsibilities includes provision of clinical input into mental health services for older adults in inpatient and community settings in the Bridgend County Borough area, under the direction of Consultants Dr Timothy Chan and Dr Pravir Prasad. This will include the responsibility for the prevention, diagnosis and management of illness.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Timothy Chan&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Consultant Psychiatrist in Old Age Psychiatry&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;timothy.chan@wales.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;01656 752881&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Pravir Prasad Tel: (01656) 752884 Email: pravirshanker.prasad@wales.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
